flagTile

void flagTile(MinesweeperTile tile)
Flags a tile on the board. Flagging means the user thinks there is a bomb at that spot. Flagging a tile will marked the tile as flagged.

Parameters:
tile - A valid reference to a title on the board

flagTile

void flagTile(int x,
              int y)
Flags a tile on the board. Flagging means the user thinks there is a bomb at that spot. Flagging a tile will marked the tile as flagged.

Parameters:
x - A valid X position between 0 and size - 1
y - A valid Y position between 0 and size - 1

clickTile

void clickTile(MinesweeperTile tile)
Clicks a tile on the board. Clicking means the user thinks there is no bomb at that spot. Clicking a title exposes the tile and may change the game state if it is a bomb.

Parameters:
tile - A valid reference to a title on the board
